{"tid":168477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【休班警又拎一分】油尖休班警遺失委任證　警方籲市民拾獲交還","createTime":"2017-03-23T14:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T15:34:24.000Z","uid":26769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79658920672a71035c377fc75f225bfa67d39d87","tid":168477,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/483312/xlarge/0762da9ff152dadeecba9b2ba33983b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F483312%2Fxlarge%2F0762da9ff152dadeecba9b2ba33983b2.jpg&h=6cb42d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼早前有警員遺失警用手機、警車車匙，今再有休班警遺失警察委任證！一名隸屬油尖警區的休班警於昨（22日）遺失一張警察委任證，案件列作「遺失政府財物」，呼籲市民如拾獲該警察委任證，應立即致電999，並把該警察委任證交到就近的警署。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，就人員對警察委任證的保管有嚴格的規定。<br />\n<br />\n相關文章<br />\n當更警車車長遺失車匙　警方籲市民拾獲交回<br />\n警察執勤遺失手機　警方籲市民交回<br />\n警員行動後遺失手扣　警方呼籲市民如拾獲應交還"},{"pid":"964c4d9908eb3d1ef38965de15a00fd99bacc6bf","tid":168477,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"遲早唔見手扣唔見槍"},{"pid":"72c249de1a9b1e39687c3fd1cc22a6a2bc2cf864","tid":168477,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲早唔見手扣唔見槍</blockquote><br />\n睇相關文章<br />\n早排已經唔見過手扣"},{"pid":"cfd26dfedd6d2f5f610072cd38d56137ecbb8a56","tid":168477,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:42:54.000Z","msg":"阿sir唔見嘢唔洗你教"},{"pid":"bf673bc812a13d755f8bdb0fd0bd63336ebb81b7","tid":168477,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遲早唔見手扣唔見槍</blockquote><br />\n睇相關文章<br />\n早排已經唔見過手扣</blockquote><br />\n係喎"},{"pid":"45b95d15b651f439ba5ef010c483477831efa773","tid":168477,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"851489780175fc8a88c12e9aad5b82cfe5f862df","tid"